Hardware Acceleration
=====================
The new hardware acceleration feature is a bit tricky. It depends a lot on the hardware used, I cannot buy and test all possible types. So I'll have to rely on you to report your issues so we can iron them out.

The FFmpeg API we can use several types of graphics adapters:

VAAPI: Intel
VDPAU: Nividia, AMD
OpenMAX: Encoding on Raspberry
MMAL: Decoding on Raspberry

